{"tid":1643950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髪族喺警總星期六開始靜坐48小時","createTime":"2019-10-10T11:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T05:52:49.000Z","uid":276684,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"757078ea12680a716380d60a7a4df8811f4783d4","tid":1643950,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"銀髪族警總靜坐48小時📢📢<br />\n<br />\n由於港府強行立法送中修例而引發的民主運動，發展至今已有四個多月，期間無論在港府決策不公，警察暴力襲擊市民，濫捕等等的情況越趨嚴重。我輩雖未能時刻與年青人共同在最前線抗爭，但保衛香港核心價值和年青人未來的責任卻時刻在心，不敢怠慢。<br />\n<br />\n現針對各種不公義情況，我們「銀髮族 老而不廢」將會在今個星期六舉行記者會，並進行一項抗爭運動，誠邀各銀髮參與 ，敬希垂注。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>抗議：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抗議警方濫權、濫捕、濫暴。<br />\n</span>2. <span style=\"color: red;\">反對將扣留時間由48小時改為72、96小時。<br />\n</span>3. <span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲警方遵守保護兒童權利公約<br />\n</span>[/size=5]</strong><br />\n📍<strong>10月12日（星期六）2:00pm</strong><br />\n至<br />\n📍<strong>10月14日（星期一）2:00pm</strong><br />\n<br />\n地點：<strong>警總</strong><br />\n<br />\n⚠️呼籲銀髮族前來「警總」靜坐抗議<br />\n<br />\n📌「銀髮族48小時靜坐」守則，希望能保平安啦👵🏻🧓🏻<br />\n<br />\n1. 是次並無任何大台或舉辦者<br />\n2. 請不要隨意跟隨任何自稱大台或群組Admin的指示做出違法行為<br />\n3. 如現場出現過激行為，請大家馬上離開，以察安全。<br />\n4. 請帶備水、食物、藥油、睡袋、帳篷等等...如需要。<br />\n5. 歡迎中途插入參與靜坐<br />\n6. 歡迎大家自行製作文宣品前來靜坐<br />\n7. 全程Be water<br />\n<br />\n⚠是次靜坐活動沒有申請「不反對通知書」，參與者須自行衡量及承擔風險。<br />\n<br />\n#不割蓆<br />\n#六大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/posts/906887293023429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilverhairgroup%2Fposts%2F906887293023429&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Emx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=acc7d052\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/posts/906887293023429</a>"},{"pid":"6008c9a45ea9639508819fee5f6791f0e316f535","tid":1643950,"uid":131696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"銀髮族 多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e861a240fb82f8a10834ce9dc9b5ddd72cc83e","tid":1643950,"uid":119442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:18:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你地"},{"pid":"6a01658760d404cf876e04f6926e7441fcf9b24a","tid":1643950,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"多謝銀髮族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fbe888338d66e4a64459008376c6f494ae56f1","tid":1643950,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"Support!"},{"pid":"9587e4dc1bf041f183009f68ec59d9240b1a7691","tid":1643950,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"多謝銀巴銀絲"},{"pid":"fd6ec8f06955be76b6e0ca1726fd4de34aa5bdbc","tid":1643950,"uid":79182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"作為後生仔真係唔撚知身邊啲朋友做緊乜鳩"},{"pid":"9ccf38e1c1f39c95a38326b6ba66bebc0fbf5da8","tid":1643950,"uid":123765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc25d399cff0c4173f5dc6e5354cf41a5130675","tid":1643950,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"仲勁過後生仔100倍"},{"pid":"a36943d5b67e710a7cb7060f88943dac1e0ca1fb","tid":1643950,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:21:12.000Z","msg":"48小時 我自己都唔得<br />\n銀髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eabaab4a358a4f16c77e8d9aff1dca872335b5d","tid":1643950,"uid":275435,"like":0,